{"tid":1453180,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"最黑暗一日","createTime":"2019-08-12T03:28:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T13:59:17.000Z","uid":122134,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4e15ae1750b55aa2fb82b7bbe2cce2e3ea83b188","tid":1453180,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:28:58.000Z","msg":"琴晚....真係訓唔著 <br />\n721既警黑事件<br />\n到而家811種種滅絕人性既手法<br />\n真係覺得好嬲 好撚心痛 <br />\n但又咩都做唔到<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190430/photo/bkn-20190430201512403-0430_00862_001_06p.jpg?20190430201828\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190430%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190430201512403-0430_00862_001_06p.jpg%3F20190430201828&h=01c08e2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港人到底幾時先肯還擊</strong><br />\n<br />\n而家真係水深火熱<br />\n人地警犬已經火力全開 無當我地係人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家係革命  唔再係出黎叫兩聲口號就以為贏左<br />\n<br />\n純粹搵地方宣洩下 表達少少意見<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n受傷義士<br />\n早日康復"},{"pid":"f6164791b794942ffb908dc8e675a3717c590867","tid":1453180,"uid":281584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:29:27.000Z","msg":"起義"},{"pid":"edf59683c8f61a50882b2caaaf8cdf827761acaa","tid":1453180,"uid":227699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e15ae1750b55aa2fb82b7bbe2cce2e3ea83b188","tid":1453180,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:28:58.000Z","msg":"琴晚....真係訓唔著 <br />\n721既警黑事件<br />\n到而家811種種滅絕人性既手法<br />\n真係覺得好嬲 好撚心痛 <br />\n但又咩都做唔到<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190430/photo/bkn-20190430201512403-0430_00862_001_06p.jpg?20190430201828\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190430%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190430201512403-0430_00862_001_06p.jpg%3F20190430201828&h=01c08e2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港人到底幾時先肯還擊</strong><br />\n<br />\n而家真係水深火熱<br />\n人地警犬已經火力全開 無當我地係人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家係革命  唔再係出黎叫兩聲口號就以為贏左<br />\n<br />\n純粹搵地方宣洩下 表達少少意見<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n受傷義士<br />\n早日康復"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:32:20.000Z","msg":"所以文宣好緊要,唔好凈係自己嬲,<br />\n要令到其他人都嬲,只有全民勇武先可以"},{"pid":"7501082599495fd91fbd149cdd90c543cdd3157c","tid":1453180,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f6164791b794942ffb908dc8e675a3717c590867","tid":1453180,"uid":281584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:29:27.000Z","msg":"起義"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:32:49.000Z","msg":"其實一早已經係<br />\n但有好多人仲覺得而家未係好激進<br />\n仲係就住就住<br />\n連搭狗鐵跳閘都要諗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f8882571c1388167493dda80e67579a4abe9d97","tid":1453180,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:37:30.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"247ad043a7323f476b6d8d2bbf0d3dd9c9dde782","tid":1453180,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:38:59.000Z","msg":"10連自推"},{"pid":"cf457b887ff51d8a44ff6eb311e046c32013bc4a","tid":1453180,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:39:09.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"739770bbf85dd7cc4ebaa851957486c4556c33d0","tid":1453180,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:39:19.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"cb34c5a6d7c445c3f35419a93d74721f77e02902","tid":1453180,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:39:29.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"3abe88bc8ce649c961efd26cc172022e171937